Kubernetes -> Controller: enqueue VbsInstance reconcile
Controller -> BaseReconciler: Reconcile(request)
BaseReconciler -> ServiceManager: reconcile desired VbsInstance
group Lookup and bind
alt tracked or explicit OCI identity already exists
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetVbsInstance
else tracked identity is missing
ServiceManager -> OCI: ListVbsInstances(filters:\ncompartmentId, name, id)
alt reusable OCI resource is not found
ServiceManager -> OCI: CreateVbsInstance
loop create pending CREATING
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetVbsInstance
end
else reusable OCI resource already exists
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetVbsInstance
end
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: persist resolved OCI identity in status
end
alt delete requested
group Delete
ServiceManager -> OCI: DeleteVbsInstance
ServiceManager -> OCI: confirm delete via GetVbsInstance or\nListVbsInstances
loop delete pending DELETING
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetVbsInstance or ListVbsInstances
end
alt cleanup or finalizer release is blocked
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: retain delete state and retry
else delete completion observed
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: release finalizer after delete completion
end
end
else OCI state is retryable
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: requeue while OCI remains in\nCREATING, UPDATING, DELETING
else live state requires field-aware\ndrift evaluation
group Drift handling
note over ServiceManager,OCI
Supported update surface: definedTags,
displayName, freeformTags,
isResourceUsageAgreementGranted (+1
more)
Reject before mutate: force-new fields
compartmentId, name
Lookup filters: compartmentId, name, id
Lookup matching: exact compartmentId
plus name unique match in ACTIVE,
CREATING, or UPDATING; duplicate matches
fail
end note
opt force-new or conflicting drift is detected
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: reject before OCI mutation
end
opt supported mutable drift is detected
ServiceManager -> OCI: Apply ChangeVbsInstanceCompartment,\nUpdateVbsInstance only for mutable\nfields definedTags, displayName,\nfreeformTags,\nisResourceUsageAgreementGranted (+1\nmore)
loop update pending UPDATING
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetVbsInstance
end
end
ServiceManager -> OCI: run helper hooks\ncreate=tfresource.CreateResource,\ntfresource.WaitForWorkRequestWithErrorHandling\nentity=vbsinstance action=CREATED;\nupdate=tfresource.UpdateResource,\ntfresource.WaitForWorkRequestWithErrorHandling\nentity=vbsinstance action=UPDATED;\ndelete=tfresource.DeleteResource,\ntfresource.WaitForWorkRequestWithErrorHandling\nentity=vbsinstance action=DELETED
ServiceManager -> OCI: apply follow-up strategy\ncreate=GetWorkRequest ->\nGetVbsInstance;\nupdate=GetWorkRequest ->\nGetVbsInstance;\ndelete=GetWorkRequest ->\nGetVbsInstance/ListVbsInstances\nconfirm-delete
end
ServiceManager --> BaseReconciler: status=required,\nfinalizer=retain-until-confirmed-delete
end
BaseReconciler --> Controller: requeue on provisioning, updating,\nterminating
